# Planning 
UniWell:A Health Tracker for SDG3: Good Health and Well-being.

# Problem statement
Students face difficulties in monitoring their daily health habits. Emergencies also make it difficult for the students to seek
medical attention on time.

# Objective
Our objective is to create a daily haelth logging for the students. This will include water intake, sleep hours, exercising and meal intakes.
UniWell will enable the student to log their daily health habits. This will help the students to maintain a healthy lifestyles. The students will also
be able to seek medical atention on time in case of an emergency.

# Scope
The project will include the following:
- Authentication: Secure Login, Create a Password, Password Reset.
- Health Records: Input daily water intake, sleeping hours, exercising, and meal intakes.
- Data Visualization: Dashboard Summary, Weekly Averages.
- Smart Reminders: Send reminders for data that has not been recorded.
- Admin Functions: Account Management, Health Tips Pulishing, Statistical Reports, System Monitoring.

# Timeline
- Week 1: Planning and requirements.
- Week 2: Design(wireframes and diagrams).
- Week 3: Development.
- Week 4: Testing and Finalization.

